TONIGHT!
.
Join us for the May Commercial/Print night, The LOWEST priced commercial networking event in the industry!
.
If you want to break into commercials, this is the event for you. Whether it's on-camera or in a magazine, there are no age, size, or height restrictions and both actors and "real people" (non-actors) are welcome.  In one evening, actors get to meet and audition for top commercial agents and casting directors. As well as reading for all of our guests, attendees are welcome to leave with them their head shots.
•
This is the most efficient platform for actors to get on the radar of NYC's top commercial industry. All of our events have success stories, from actors who get called in for the first time to those who start freelancing to those who book jobs and get signed.
.
Date: Wednesday, May 17th 2017
﻿Time﻿:﻿ 7PM-830PM
﻿Location:﻿ Simple Studios, 134 West 29th Street, 2nd Floor, NYC
More info/book: http://www.theactorsgreenroom.com/may-commercialprint-night.html
